<img width="417" height="350" alt="Image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/e649b879-861b-4efd-9b35-2fc54b9d3a3d" />

Only the 3D component appears.

<img width="268" height="166" alt="Image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/13f626f7-2913-4cd6-a105-6fab0531a48b" />

The script appears like this:

```csharp
