FishNet.Managing.Scened.SceneManager+<__LoadScenes>d__109.MoveNext () (at Assets/FishNet/Runtime/Managing/Scened/SceneManager.cs:1253)
```
Suggested fix for issue 1: NetworkObject.GetNetworkObjects():

```
if (option.FastContains(GetNetworkObjectOption.RuntimeNested))
{
    if (RuntimeChildNetworkBehaviours != null)
    {
        foreach (NetworkBehaviour nb in RuntimeChildNetworkBehaviours)
            cache.Add(nb.NetworkObject);
    }
    includesNested = true;
}


if (option.FastContains(GetNetworkObjectOption.InitializedNested))
{
    if (InitializedNestedNetworkObjects != null)
        cache.AddRangeUnique(InitializedNestedNetworkObjects);
    includesNested = true;
}
```
Suggested fix for issue 2: SceneManager.MoveClientHostObjects():
```

foreach (NetworkObject nob in NetworkManager.ServerManager.Objects.Spawned.Values)
{
    if (nob == null)
        continue;
    // ... rest of loop
}
```
